    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to even post this, but life moves on and it\u2019s time for this absolute beauty to find a new home. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s spent almost its whole life tucked away in the garage, only coming out for those perfect sunny afternoon drives. It\u2019s in truly incredible shape, looking and feeling just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. You won\u2019t find a speck of dust on the engine, and the paint still has that deep, mirror-like shine that turns heads at every stoplight. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate it just as much as I have. Come by, let's chat cars, and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your dream ride!",
